Located in Muradnagar, Stanza Living’s Maputo House is a tastefully designed, fully furnished residence for boys. With all-inclusive services like food, house-keeping, laundry, maintenance, security and more, you can experience a hassle-free stay. We also bring you an exciting array of engaging social events, exclusive brand partnerships and professional programmes so your student days can be the most enjoyable time of your lives. 
We believe, that you should never have to deal with an unprofessional or poorly managed PG or hostel. With Stanza Living you can end your hunt for the best PG in the region.
